room_title: Escape room "Espionage" by 5 Wits in Syracuse
room_description: The fate of the world is in your hands! Get your hands on cracking safes, hacking computers and dodging lasers as your crew goes head to head with the notorious CABAL corporation. Every puzzle you solve, every challenge you conquer, and every mistake you make will change the outcome, so stay sharp, move fast - and don't get caught!
